{"tid":343550,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"【摩門戀】公主道上與天使訂立永恆婚約","createTime":"2017-08-01T14:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T14:34:34.000Z","uid":45389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7c34c09f1486ee0aa4eeb202dd73249b09523003","tid":343550,"uid":45389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:20:35.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">天使之戀第三部</div><br />\n<br />\nA dramatic love story between a Mormon girl and a Mormon boy.<br />\n<br />\n在下都估唔到，當初只係番工坐太耐車想搵啲世藝搞下，就用手機寫下彤彤既故事，最後居然會走到呢一步，可以出到《天使之戀》三部曲。<br />\n<br />\n我知道今次我咁寫，會引起好大既爭議，就算係有人會見到個標題就直接睇都唔睇比個負皮我，我都毫無怨言。其不相瞞，我有戴過黑牌起香港生活過，我知道自己環境係點。<br />\n<br />\n我之所以咁寫，係因為我一直都想以咁既形式將第三位天使既愛情故事呈現出黎，呢個係我最大既心願；再者，人最大既痛苦莫過於違背自己既信仰，如果我因為驚正負數失衡，或者因為驚比人認出自己係Mormon，就放棄Mormon呢個background setting既話，我內心將會承受既無法形容既痛苦，到時間再多既正評都冇辦法令我開心。<br />\n<br />\n但無論如何，在下只希望可以開心見誠地同大家交流。在下衷心感謝各位支持天使們同在下既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n(本故事同第一、第二季基本上無關聯，冇睇過之前兩季並唔會影響對劇情既理解)<br />\n<br />\n紙言同步：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/article/130527/%E3%80%90%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%BF%E4%B9%8B%E6%88%80-III%E3%80%91%E3%80%8A%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%BB%E9%81%93%E4%B8%8A%E8%88%87%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%BF%E8%A8%82%E7%AB%8B%E6%B0%B8%E6%81%86%E5%A9%9A%E7%B4%84%E3%80%8B.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Farticle%2F130527%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%2588%2580-III%25E3%2580%2591%25E3%2580%258A%25E5%2585%25AC%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%2581%2593%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E8%25A8%2582%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E6%2581%2586%25E5%25A9%259A%25E7%25B4%2584%25E3%2580%258B.html&d=eThoJcB1ACfYqYpccgV6Hm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=8a92fd92\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/article/130527/%E3%80%90%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%BF%E4%B9%8B%E6%88%80-III%E3%80%91%E3%80%8A%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%BB%E9%81%93%E4%B8%8A%E8%88%87%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%BF%E8%A8%82%E7%AB%8B%E6%B0%B8%E6%81%86%E5%A9%9A%E7%B4%84%E3%80%8B.html</a><br />\n<br />\n在下的紙言專頁( 內有天使之戀第一部及第二部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  )：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/author/14541/%E7%90%B4%E8%A1%80.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Fauthor%2F14541%2F%25E7%2590%25B4%25E8%25A1%2580.html&d=eThoJcB1ACfYqYpccgV6Hm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=1a0aa2ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/author/14541/%E7%90%B4%E8%A1%80.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">若然我在今生中沒有娶你為妻，與你作永恆印證的話，將來我上了天堂，每次看到你時我都會為自己在塵世中的愚蠢感到無比後悔。</span>"},{"pid":"b273753df7ef56cbaf107096d74da09ebafe16e8","tid":343550,"uid":45389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:22:48.000Z","msg":"自膠一下，未改名就開POST；從我重開過個POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c5bd00887dac18d8cbed9e266ad195e69182e3","tid":343550,"uid":45389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:34:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: maroon;\">試字顏色</span>"}]}